mixin Features1
  +Section
    .row.justify-content-center.text-center
      .col-lg-8.col-xl-7.col-xxl-6
        h1.fs-2.fs-sm-4.fs-md-5 Fully-furnished data analytics and prediction platform
        p.leadWe provide state of the art data visualizations that help you get a real view of all the trends in your business. We also provide you with the tools to predict future trends and make the right decisions.

    .row.flex-center.mt-8
      .col-md.col-lg-5.col-xl-4.ps-lg-6
        img.img-fluid.px-6.px-md-0(src=`${CWD}assets/img/icons/spot-illustrations/50.png` alt='')
      .col-md.col-lg-5.col-xl-4.mt-4.mt-md-0
        h5.text-danger
          span.far.fa-lightbulb.me-2
          | UPLOAD
        h3 Streamlined Data Processing & Organization
        p Upload files and data to the AI-powered system for automatic classification, collection, and assessment. The system leverages AI and ML algorithms to intelligently categorize and organize data, making it easier for the company to access and analyze relevant information efficiently. This feature eliminates the need for manual sorting and enhances data management capabilities.

    .row.flex-center.mt-7
      .col-md.col-lg-5.col-xl-4.pe-lg-6.order-md-2
        img.img-fluid.px-6.px-md-0(src=`${CWD}assets/img/icons/spot-illustrations/49.png` alt='')
      .col-md.col-lg-5.col-xl-4.mt-4.mt-md-0
        h5.text-info 
          span.far.fa-object-ungroup.me-2
          | COLLECT DATA, AUTOMATE TASKS
        h3 Enhanced Performance Monitoring & Workflow Optimization
        p Gain valuable insights into client applications through data collection and analysis. The AI and ML algorithms track user behavior, application performance, and other relevant metrics to provide comprehensive analytics. Additionally, the system automates repetitive tasks, freeing up valuable time for employees to focus on more strategic initiatives and improving overall operational efficiency.

    .row.flex-center.mt-7
      .col-md.col-lg-5.col-xl-4.ps-lg-6
        img.img-fluid.px-6.px-md-0(src=`${CWD}assets/img/icons/spot-illustrations/48.png` alt='')
      .col-md.col-lg-5.col-xl-4.mt-4.mt-md-0
        h5.text-success
          span.far.fa-paper-plane.me-2
          | PREDICTIONS AND ANALYTICS
        h3 Comprehensive Insights from Diverse Data Sets
        p Utilize AI and ML techniques to generate predictions and analytics based on a wide range of data sources, including excel sheets, reports, articles, and more. The system extracts relevant information, identifies patterns, and performs sophisticated analysis to deliver actionable insights. These predictive capabilities empower decision-makers to make informed choices, optimize strategies, and stay ahead of the competition.

mixin Features2
  +Section.bg-light.text-center
    .row
      .col
        h1.fs-2.fs-sm-4.fs-md-5 Here's what's in it for you
        p.lead Things you will get right out of the box with Core&amp;Outline.
    .row.mt-6
      .col-lg-4
        .card.card-span.h-100
          .card-span-img
            span.fab.fa-sass.fs-4.text-info
          .card-body.pt-6.pb-4
            h5.mb-2 Accurate Predictions for Future Insights
            p Our advanced Machine Learning models provide companies with accurate predictions that enable them to see into the future of their business.

      .col-lg-4.mt-6.mt-lg-0
        .card.card-span.h-100
          .card-span-img
            span.fab.fa-node-js.fs-5.text-success
          .card-body.pt-6.pb-4
            h5.mb-2 Comprehensive Data Analytics
            p Our data analytics capabilities go beyond simple reporting and delve into in-depth analysis.

      .col-lg-4.mt-6.mt-lg-0
        .card.card-span.h-100
          .card-span-img
            span.fab.fa-gulp.fs-6.text-danger
          .card-body.pt-6.pb-4
            h5.mb-2 Decision Making & Strategic Planning
            p With our solutions, companies can enhance their decision-making processes and strategic planning initiatives.

